{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM09_ED2_090.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x3a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "\"I want to save Nio...\" It all started<CR>from there. A journey with one goal. But<CR>in that time, Ayesha had a rapid growth."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "A living legend who knows and does<CR>everything. That was how she was<CR>perceived in this age."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Finding success in every field, she<CR>eventually became a famous leader by<CR>restoring alchemy to this land..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x44,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it's Lady Ayesha!<CR>Lady Ayesha has arrived!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x45,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Her divinity... She's like a goddess from ancient myths."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x46,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Look Mom, it's Lady Ayesha!<CR>Lady Ayesha came to see us!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x47,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes, how amazing it is that Lady Ayesha would come to our town...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Come on, Lady Ayesha, everyone is calling for you. You should wave to them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "S-Stop calling me that, Nio..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sorry. But see? It looks like everyone's waiting for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* No matter how many times they treat me like this, I'll never get used to it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I haven't done anything to deserve this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Nobody else seems to agree with you. Your medicine is amazing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I just want to lock myself up in the workshop and synthesize..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No whining. Hurry, wave your hand!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "They kindly held a grand ceremony to welcome us."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Haha... Okay..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x44,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ooh! Lady Ayesha is waving to us!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x48,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Lady Ayesha is so marvelous!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x49,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "My, my, how fortunate. Now my back pain will be cured!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x4a,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "There's no doubt our farm will have a good harvest this year! Oh, heaven be praised!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x4b,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, Lady Ayesha! How beautiful..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ha, haha, hahahaha...ha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x43,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Lady Sage Ayesha! Welcome to our town!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x43,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We are extremely honored to have you go to the trouble of coming here today!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "How kind of you. Then without any further delay, can you tell us your story?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x43,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Certainly. Our town is currently being threatened by a mysterious, black slag."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x43,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Our fields have been ravaged and our children are unable to play outside."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x43,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If you could please, with Lady Ayesha's power, rescue our‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sis, what do you think?<CR>Can you defeat it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I think it'll be easy, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Got it! Just leave it to us. We shall exterminate that slag by the end of the day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x43,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, how reassuring your words are! Everybody, it is as you heard!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x43,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Our town will be saved! By the hands of Lady Ayesha, the evil slag will be slain!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x4b,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ohh, Lady Ayesha! Thank you so much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x44,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, now our town is virtually saved. No, it has already been saved!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x4a,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Heaven be praised..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Umm, you don't have to be that humble..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x47,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If you do something naughty, I'm gonna have Lady Ayesha scold you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x46,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I won't do anything for Lady Ayesha to scold me about."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ahh...no one's listening to me. What should I do...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hey, Nio. I just want to help people normally..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Why do people always get so excited?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's because you're so awesome, Sis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* But I'm not. I'm just a regular apothecary."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I kept telling them that in the beginning, but nooo one listened."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But, it'll be fine, as long as we don't get carried away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Even with a royal welcome, we'll be able to keep going without losing sight of ourselves."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ugh, I'm happy that they're happy,<CR>but I'd still prefer \"normal\"..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x4a,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, seeing Lady Ayesha smile, I feel like it's added 50 years to my life."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x44,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "All hail Lady Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x45,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "All hail Lady Ayesha!"
        },
